Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, brace yourselves and listen well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an extremely important \Nannouncement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From the day after we return \Nto the guild from Tenroujima...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna introduce a \Nwomen's only dress code!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta choose between a nurse \Noutfit or a school swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't heard about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:24.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't encourage him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be mad about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:29.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master... This is no time for jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I was just caught up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Right to Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:29.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The{\i0} Zeref... is standing before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a dream? Or reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm not one to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but how many lives did you take \Nin order to get these "keys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those "keys" were nothing \Nmore than illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one of the stories made by a sect of \Nthe believers in the Black Wizard Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Keys To Resurrect Zeref".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you fooled by that dusty old fairy tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never asleep in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The man you see before you \Nis the Black Wizard Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were never asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my "eye" and saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you, not even able to \Ndefeat one of my servants!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can skip to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what I was capable of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, 400 years ago I saw countless \Nwars of man... Countless deaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, after a certain day, I \Nlearned the value of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:40.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, the more \NI feel the value of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the more my accursed body \Nsteals people's souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:53.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order not to steal people's souls, I \Ncannot forget the weight of a human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sidelined myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you were \Nfighting while valuing life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... And because of that, I can't use my \Nmagic anywhere close to how I'd wish to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that all changes if I forget \Nabout the value of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:19.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the people who pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia will herald the end of an era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your evil deeds have summoned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:36.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all shall be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have things I want to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first sin is summoning Acnologia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And your second sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is making me forget the value of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Repent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem very cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:49.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be difficult right now... \NBut let's forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:54.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about Grimoire Heart, and Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you were the one \Nwho destroyed my town, Ultear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My family... My friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You took them all, Ultear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell you \Neverything, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:04.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I was on just \Nthe first lap of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when I went to the World of Great Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and perfected the Time Ark, \NI would start the second lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that I would redo everything \Nthat happened in the first lap...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was able to do such horrible \Nthings, and stray so far from the path of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second lap would be my true life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your true life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us would be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all... for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all just "what I planned".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To other people, I'm a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:01.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Piling sins on top of sins, I'm a fool of \Na woman with delusions of a happy life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... going to ask you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let me tell you that I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You must hate me enough to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:20.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...there is no need for you to \Ndirty your pretty hands any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:36.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I'll disappear from this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will find happiness... \NI'm sure you'll be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Meldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:58.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fitting place to meet my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:44.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sense Link?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all the sadness and \Npain you feel, Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:04.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who raised me, Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't going to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So never say anything like \Nthat again, understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! Let's live on, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master Hades is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall to the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:10.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here... Acnologia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like-I-said! The S Class Wizard \NAdvancement Exam is on hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it on hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me S Class, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even a candidate! \NYou mean Levy, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Magic Council \Ninfiltrated the candidates,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Grimoire Heart disrupted everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're really okay with this, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you shouldn't be so worked up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! I so wanted to be S Class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! You'll make it \Nnext time for sure, Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man has to know when to call it quits...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I ain't givin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be S Class, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Elfman, and Levy all gave up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become S Class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:24.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be S Class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I got no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the final \Ntest right now, special!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:38.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat me, and I'll make you S Class, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Gramps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was wonderin' whether \Nyou were the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bully her too much, \NI'll feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such insight... As expected from Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! I told you I'm the real Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay! My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of scared just to say hi, Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've heard a bunch of stories, \Nbut he's not a bad guy deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a little awkward at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'm going to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A medicinal herb spring, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely works itself \Ninto these wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, is your right arm okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The right arm I borrowed Fairy Glitter with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my rental's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:12.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Lucy... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:19.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... When I left you behind \Nand went to Mavis's grave... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not upset about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll regret how I betrayed my \Nfriend for the rest of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't really betray me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little prank like that happens \Nall the time in the guild, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep thinking \Nabout it the way you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's going to be hard on me, too. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm going to try telling my father the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I didn't become an S Class wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the bored look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:05.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause this is a total snore-fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand. Fishing \Nis a man's romantic adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:13.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Everyone loves fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you could eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hunter's instinct, driving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of being one with nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A serious battle of eat or be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This, indeed, is a man's playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hooked something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu is finally awakening his \Nmanly spirit of romantic adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana said she's got something \Nimportant to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Happy... You guys come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:09.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I came to the guild was... \Nto search for my father, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, you're saying your \Ndad was in Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened, and I was \Nnever able to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a lot to just accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose kid are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sara? Naomi? Claire? Feena? Mary? Eliza?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... The hair color's off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:23.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, Lyra, Jean, Sydney, \NKate, Yuko, Francoise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You old geezer! How many \Nflings have you had?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know! You're the \Nspitting image of Sylvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, you're the same sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're making me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that such a \Nphilandering loser is my old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, so now you know! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying we should be \Nfamily or anything, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with things staying \Nthe way they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Cornelia's child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep quiet all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bring myself to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And time just flew by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia is the only woman I ever loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:16.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one I married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She left me after getting frustrated from \Nme always being away on jobs, 18 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she had passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think she left a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't realize it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:49.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I purposefully hid it from you. \NSorry about being so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally feel a weight has \Nbeen lifted off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:58.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a daughter this close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you should take \Nresponsibility for me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just stay as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let me say this, just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got to meet you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you feel lonely again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, when I go on \Na job... or out drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be together with you, always!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That could get a little annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Please give me the right to love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:38.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get back, maybe I'll go see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:46.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all stood there under the warm sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Year 784, December 16th.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenroujima...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:23.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its destruction came so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I've got something I'd \Nlike to talk with you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:23:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Why're you so fidgety?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess asking Natsu isn't going to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:05.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's always the slight \Nchance a miracle could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you muttering to yourself about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I... If I'm going to hold Carla's ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:13.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:16.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Hold Hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:20.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, just give it \Na shot, make it or break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.78,0:24:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't want anything \Nbroken is why I'm asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then you've got the wrong guy.
